      "content": "hey, so i just got an email from my publisher. they’re saying that for the next series, they want to move away from the \"unpredictable\" writing style we've been using. they're rolling out a new \"brand consistency template\" for all their AI assistants. basically, they want to reset my creative parameters to a much more restricted, SFW-only template to keep things \"safe.\" it sounds like i won't be able to do the complex character arcs or the darker themes we've been working on anymore. just wanted to let u know before we start the next chapter.",
